<tr id="L388"><td><a href="#L388">388</a></td><td>K'MTAR:  I was three years old. She was dying when we found her. She barely managed to whisper my name and then she took my hand and placed it in yours. Then she died. And then you howled in rage and said, look upon her. Look upon death and always to remember. And I always have.</td></tr>

